```{r DataImports+InitialLoads}
    install.packages("ggplot2")
    library(ggplot2)
    install.packages("dplyr")
    library(dplyr)
    NYData <- read.csv("NYAPDatasetCSV.csv")
    
    NYDataAllStudents <- NYData %>% 
      filter(
        aggregation_code == "0",
        SUBGROUP_NAME == "All Students")
    NYDataDivided <- NYData %>% 
      filter(
        aggregation_code == "0",
        SUBGROUP_NAME != "All Students")
    rm(NYData)
```
